# ==============================================================================
# CODEOWNERS — Defines who is responsible for code review across the repo.
#
# WHY: Ensures the right people review changes in their area of expertise.
# GitHub automatically requests reviews from matching owners when a PR
# touches files matching these patterns.
#
# SYNTAX: Each line is a pattern followed by one or more GitHub usernames
# or team names. Later rules override earlier ones (more specific wins).
#
# See: https://docs.github.com/en/repositories/managing-your-repositorys-settings-and-features/customizing-your-repository/about-code-owners
# ==============================================================================

